short of the eight votes needed to override an agnos veto 
at saturdays eighthour meeting business and labor leaders 
agreed to implement the law in three stages 
first any new equipment purchased one year or more after the 
law is adopted must conform to the new standards 
within 30 months businesses must bring most workstations into 
conformance with vdt safety standards 
if doing so costs more than 250 those businesses will have an 
additional 18 months to comply 
the law applies to companies with 15 or more employees it also 
creates an advisory panel to monitor research about possible 
radiation hazards and other heath effects from vdt use 
