tips and practical advice for journalists 
steffens has been news editor of the daily view section of the 
los angeles times orange county edition supervising production 
he previously was graphics editor of the la times orange county 
edition and from 1984 to 1987 he was assistant managing editor for 
graphics at the san diego union 
