i dont know that id classify that as secrecy he said 
for many soldiers homesickness and anxiety were heightened by 
the higher state of alert just three weeks before the un jan 15 
deadline for iraq to withdraw its troops from kuwait 
military sources speaking on condition of anonymity said the 
alert was ordered because of fears of a terrorist attack over the 
christmas holidays 
