<TEXT>
iranian officials and lebanese shiite 
moslem fundamentalists have said for months that western hostages 
would be freed before the years end but as the days dwindle so 
do hopes 
five hostages held by proiranian extremists were freed during 
the year but 13 remain in captivity and there is no indication 
they will be released by jan 1 
hopes that all hostages might be freed this year followed 
improvements in irans relations with the west following the death 
