fruit flies like a banana 
what blue poison dart frogs like is a diet high in calcium and 
phosphorous humidity and privacy the threequarterinch 
blueandblack frog is sonamed because it secretes a deadly 
alkaloid similar to curare which south american indians use to 
make poison darts 
in the wild they lay their eggs under large jungle leaves 
cover says weve found the bottom of 2liter soda bottles are a 
real good breeding hut we put a plastic leaf in a petri dish and 
put the bottle over the top 
the male does a courtship dance the female if receptive 
follows him in and does an elaborate courtship dance with all kinds 
of stroking and spinning then she lays her eggs and hell 
fertilize them 
