concert mae west who got a life jacket named for her prow was 
beloved by the crew for her large tips and the final night party 
she threw for waiters and stewards who served her 
the evenlarger queen elizabeth down to two stacks made her 
debut in time to don gray livery and go off to war as a troopship 
zigzagging and outspeeding submarines the queens delivered 
millions of british and commonwealth soldiers to every war zone 
transporting whole us divisions for the normandy invasion 
the mary once packed 16683 aboard the queens in winston 
churchills estimation shortened the war in europe by at least a 
year the uboats never got close but there was one tragedy when 
the queen mary in rough seas collided with her escort hms curacao 
slicing the cruiser in half wartime rules did not permit 
endangering her prime cargo of 15000 soldiers by picking up 
survivors 
the united states paid cunard 91 million for deploying 16 
