could never operate cruise schedules around the world without it 
cunard has seven cruise ships calling at 240 ports around the 
world and the qe2 still keeps up a semblance of transatlantic 
service with 18 crossings a year 
contrary to an unsinkable legend cunard captains throughout the 
lines history have rarely been called on to perform marriages 
brakstad who has been a captain for half of his 56 years has 
yet to tie any marital knots but he does have a plaque in his sea 
cabin that reads all marriages performed by this captain are 
valid only for the duration of the voyage 
