recycler warner bros zz top 
 
billy gibbons dusty hill and frank beard still are mining the 
old boogie rock to which they first staked their claim to stardom 
more than 10 years ago 
and it still works the style wears as well as a pair of boots 
that never seem too tired for another stomp around the dance floor 
